K A T S U 🐥 Everyone is always eating at @wagamama_uk 😋 I'm constantly seeing hashtags and check in to this place 🤗 And it does look delicious 🤤 I'm a foodie and LOVE eating out at any opportunity I get 🙈 I've had a look at the menu 🍱🍣🍛 And something that has caught my eye is This beauty 👉🏽 It's called Katsu curry 🍛 and it looks amazing 😻 There is so many #katsucurry on #instagram 🤔 So I'm only assuming it's a very popular dish people order a lot 👍🏽 So I've done my research to see how many syns this contains.. 😱 A WHOPPING 27 SYNS 😱😓 That's almost 2 full days of your syn allowance in 1 meal 😮😖 So me being me, I'm going to try and recreate this into @slimmingworld friendly dish 👍🏽👍🏽 It appears to be a new very popular dish 🍴in the @slimmingworld dimension too 💪🏿👌🏾 So this evenings dinner will be KATSU CURRY 🍛 I will try and make it SYN FREE! And add as much SS 🥑🥕🌽🥒🍆🍅 food as possible without changing the taste too much 👅 I like to try and create meals we feel guilty eating but without feeling guilty 🙌🏽 Will post a step by step on my story later and pics of the created plate of heaven ✨✨ 😋 #slimmingworlduk #slimmingworld #swblogger #swblogging #blogger #blog #vlogging #vlogger #bloggerlife #swposts #weightloss #weightlosstransformation #weightlossjourney #weightlossinspo #maintained #nogain #onplan #slimmingworldfollowers #sp #eesp #ee #extraeasy #Summerbody #katsucurry #swmafia #swmafiauk #inspiration

L A Y E R S O F L O V E 🥓🍳 Breakfast is my favourite meal of the day 📅 (When it involves bacon 🥓 and eggs 🍳😋) It sets you up for most of the day 👩🏽‍🍳 without craving sugary rubbish post lunch/afternoon 👊🏾 When everyone thinks "fry up" they automatically think grease 🤐 Which in most cases is the case 🤢 BUT you can make a "fry up" healthy and SYN FREE 😮😱 @frylighthq is the best alternative to oil 🍶 and its not greasy at all 👊🏾 So don't think you can't enjoy your Family Saturday morning fry up 🥓🍳 Because you can 😋👍🏽 Just make the right choices and the results will follow 👉🏽 #slimmingworlduk #slimmingworld #swblogger #swblogging #blogger #blog #vlogging #vlogger #bloggerlife #swposts #weightloss #weightlosstransformation #weightlossjourney #weightlossinspo #maintained #nogain #onplan #slimmingworldfollowers #sp #eesp #ee #extraeasy #Summerbody #breakfast #eggsontoast #baconontoast #eggsandbaconontoast #inspiration #inspire #inspiring
